title: Journal of the American Institute of Electrical Engineers

preceded-by.note: Proceedings of the American Institute of Electrical Engineers

additional-note: Some issues after 1923 use 'Journal of the A.I.E.E' on covers and 'Journal of the American Institute of Electrical Engineers' on inside pages. Issues before 1924 also use 'Journal of A.I.E.E.' or similar in running page headers.
